Paper: hep-th/0302036

Date: 2003-02-06

Title: Twisting kappa-deformed phase space

Authors: Piotr Czerhoniak (Institute of Physics, Zielona Gora Univ.)

Comments: LaTeX, 24 pages, 2 references added

We discuss the twisting procedure applied to the kappa-deformed space-time.Two kinds of twisttings are considered, for both we introduce related phasespaces. The changes of duality relations under the action of twist are shown.